{
  "stem": "22892.7",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there was the big thing, and they would talk about things until the point I got-- and I told them, when it was convenient for me to upset them, then I said, I'm not German.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm a Jew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That upset them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they thought, oh, Miller, and, you know, maybe they thought I looked German, too.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I spoke German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I-- it's strange-- there was not-- there was no hatred.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, I despised some of the things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I just didn't carry that hatred with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In a way, I-- I was glad, because of some-- but I also didn't have great respect for them, for another, you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But considering the alternative to be in Korea, I was happy to be in Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And things looked bad then, because there could have been a war with the Russians at any time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The relations were not good, the Berlin blockade, and all kinds of things went on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were constantly preparing for war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I probably thought we wouldn't have a [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "China's ?] chance if there was a war in-- in Germany, because the Russians were so huge, with their land armies.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they could overrun that part of Europe anyway.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I hoped there would-- wouldn't be a war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I became corporal, and then they froze rank.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I-- I-- I was a corporal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was a gunner-- was-- and the machine-- machine gun was my thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, you, as an infantry man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we were constantly on maneuvers, constantly in the field.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You come in to clean up and take a break and back in the field.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were constantly on training, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] preparing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
